such mitigation here seem suspect. Dominic, as presented by Dante,
is a tough warrior whom the poet goes out of his way also to present
as a 'lover'". Infatti Domenico non @e presentato come amante della
povert@a, sebbene non la disdegni, ma della |fede; ~a ci@o si aggiunge
